org.projectfloodlight.openflow.types

Class OFVlanVidMatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.projectfloodlight.openflow.types.OFVlanVidMatch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<OFVlanVidMatch>, OFValueType<OFVlanVidMatch>, PrimitiveSinkable

    public class OFVlanVidMatch
extends Object
implements OFValueType<OFVlanVidMatch>
    Represents an OpenFlow Vlan VID for use in Matches, as specified by the OpenFlow 1.3 spec. Note: this is not just the 12-bit vlan tag. OpenFlow defines the additional mask bits 0x1000 to represent the presence of a vlan tag. This additional bit will be stripped when writing a OF1.0 value tag.
    Author:
    Andreas Wundsam <andreas.wundsam@bigswitch.com>
